data.name: Form_Text.Text
data.value: This is a tool for generating the code that helps KF2 find your custom maps, useful for servers with lots of maps! The issue with doing this manually is that it takes time, and you can easilly make mistakes, now this takes the hastle out of all of that! Simply select the directory the custom maps are stored and then click Go! a text file shall be produced with the code you need.
